nodes.text: Prita Sven was a female, whom at one point was a regional administrator in the Galactic Empire, later becoming Vice Grand Administrator of stormtrooper recruitment. Prior to her time as Vice Grand Administrator, Prita met with Lando Calrissian on Pantora and was persuaded into letting him fly offplanet with a freighter full of illegally poached forlyn carcasses.
Prita Sven first appeared in the 2018 canon novel, Last Shot, written Daniel José Older. Sven is incorrectly referred to as Vice Admiral Sven at one point in the novel.
